'''极端民族主义'''（{{lang-en|Ultranationalism}}，也译为'''超国家主义'''<ref>{{cite journal |author1=汪宏倫 |title=從《戰爭論》到《新歷史教科書》：試論日本當代民族主義的怨恨心態及其制度成因 |journal=台灣社會學 |date=2010-06 |issue=十九 |pages=148-200 |url=https://www.ios.sinica.edu.tw/journal/ts-19/19-4_full_text.pdf |accessdate=2020-08-24 |archive-date=2021-05-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210527111955/https://www.ios.sinica.edu.tw/journal/ts-19/19-4_full_text.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>或'''超民族主义'''<ref>{{cite journal |author1=白永瑞 |title=东亚地域秩序: 超越帝国, 走向东亚共同体 |journal=《思想》 |date=2006年9月 |issue=3 |pages=36-44 |url=http://www.shehui.pku.edu.cn/upload/editor/file/20180829/20180829111529_1818.pdf |accessdate=2020-08-24 |archive-date=2021-05-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210527111955/http://www.shehui.pku.edu.cn/upload/editor/file/20180829/20180829111529_1818.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>）是一种极端的[[民族主義|民族主义]]，将一国或一族人的利益置于所有他人之上，或简单的说是“對自己民族極端的崇拜”（extreme devotion to one's own nation）。<ref>[https://en.oxforddictionaries.com/definition/us/ultranationalism Ultranationalism] {{Wayback|url=https://en.oxforddictionaries.com/definition/us/ultranationalism |date=20190512054437 }}. Oxford English Dictionary. Retrieved 29 June 2017.</ref><ref>[https://www.collinsdictionary.com/dictionary/english/ultranationalism Ultranationalism] {{Wayback|url=https://www.collinsdictionary.com/dictionary/english/ultranationalism |date=20190512054436 }}. Collins English Dictionary. Retrieved 29 June 2017.</ref>

极端民族主义与国家复兴是[[法西斯主义|法西斯主义]]的关键基础。<ref>Roger Griffin, "Nationalism" in Cyprian Blamires, ed., ''World Fascism: A Historical Encyclopedia'', vol. 2 (Santa Barbara, California: ABC-CLIO, 2006), pp. 451–53.</ref>

根据{{le|加努斯·布加杰斯基|Janusz Bugajski}}的说法，在最极端或发展到终极形态时，极端民族主义类似于法西斯主义，其特点是[[仇外|仇外]]蔑视，支持[[威权主义|专制]]政治并靠近[[極權主義|极权主义]] ，强调[[魅力型權威|魅力型领袖]]，一个组织上无定形的运动型政党，以及国家之间的“有机统一”。 <ref>[https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=xeFNV40_EUAC&pg=PA65&dq=ultranationalism+authoritarian&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwi20tfP0rnaAhWLOsAKHQhhB7wQ6AEIWDAI#v=onepage&q&f=false ''The Politics of National Minority Participation in Post-communist Europe''] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=xeFNV40_EUAC&pg=PA65&dq=ultranationalism+authoritarian&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwi20tfP0rnaAhWLOsAKHQhhB7wQ6AEIWDAI#v=onepage&q&f=false |date=20180613160959 }}. ''EastWest Institute''. p.65. Section author - Janusz Bugajski. Book edited by Johnathan P.Stein. Published by M.E. Sharpe. Published in New York in 2000. Retrieved via Google Books.</ref>

{{le|罗杰·格里芬|Roger Griffin}}断言，极端民族主义本质上是[[仇外|仇外]]的，并且会通过神话自己历史上的伟大成就，或者强调对历史宿敌的仇恨来实现自身的合法化。它有时还会利用庸俗的体质[[人类学|人类学]]、[[遗传学|遗传学]]和[[優生學|优生学]]来对种族优越感和种族前途做合理化解释，并衬托其他种族的堕落和劣等的观念。 <ref>{{Cite book|title=World fascism: a historical encyclopedia|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=dDYRAQAAMAAJ&q=%22%22through+deeply+mythicized+narratives+of+past+cultural+or+political+periods%22&dq=%22%22through+deeply+mythicized+narratives+of+past+cultural+or+political+periods%22&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwjLpMWk1efZAhWF7lMKHSJqCZoQ6AEIKTAA|year=2006|page=452|access-date=2019-08-16|archive-date=2020-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200125041227/https://books.google.com/books?id=dDYRAQAAMAAJ&q=%22%22through+deeply+mythicized+narratives+of+past+cultural+or+political+periods%22&dq=%22%22through+deeply+mythicized+narratives+of+past+cultural+or+political+periods%22&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwjLpMWk1efZAhWF7lMKHSJqCZoQ6AEIKTAA|dead-url=no}}</ref>

